===Noun===
{{en-noun|-|s}}

# Condensed [[water]] falling from a [[cloud]].
#: ''We've been having a lot of '''rain''' lately''.
#: ''The '''rains''' came late that year.''
# {{label|en|figuratively}} Any matter moving or falling, usually through air, and especially if liquid or otherwise figuratively identifiable with [[raindrop]]s.
# {{label|en|figuratively}} An instance of [[particle]]s or larger pieces of [[matter]] moving or [[fall]]ing through [[air]].
#: ''A '''rain''' of mortar fire fell on our trenches.''

